       B(Exponent(4))     = 0. , 0. 
       C(Exponent(4))     = 0. , 0. 
       Xmax(5)        = 1.0, 1.0     # [1]   
       Exponent(5)     = 1.0 , 1.0
       B(Exponent(5))     = 0. , 0. 
       C(Exponent(5))     = 0. , 0. 
}


DopingDependence:
{   
        formula = 1 ,   1       # [1]   
  * If formula=1, model suggested by Masetti et al. is used:
  * mu_dop = mumin1 exp(-Pc/N) + (mu_const - mumin2)/(1+(N/Cr)^alpha)
  *                             - mu1/(1+(Cs/N)^beta)
  * with mu_const from ConstantMobility

       * parameter mumin1:
